Package grafioschtrader.entities

Class GTNetMessageAttempt

java.lang.Object
grafiosch.entities.BaseID<Integer>
grafioschtrader.entities.GTNetMessageAttempt
@Entity public class GTNetMessageAttempt extends BaseID<Integer>
Records individual transmission attempts for outgoing GTNet messages.

When a message requires multiple transmission attempts (as defined by repeatSendAsMany in GTNetModelHelper.GTNetMsgRequest, each attempt is recorded in this entity. This provides an audit trail for debugging transmission failures and analyzing retry patterns.

The retry mechanism is implemented via a background task that:

  • Queries messages where attempts < repeatSendAsMany and last attempt failed
  • Applies exponential backoff based on attempt number
  • Creates a new GTNetMessageAttempt record for each transmission attempt
  • Marks message as permanently failed when attempts exhausted
